      • proxyEval

        public Object proxyEval(String expression,
               Map<String,Object> vars)
                 throws Exception
        Method to eval expression. Holds many optimizations (@see noVarsEvals) and turn around for reliable usage (like engine auto restart). 1D Numeric "vars" are replaced using Java replace engine instead of R one. Intended to not interfer with current R env vars. Yes, it's hard-code :)
        Parameters:
        expression - String to evaluate
        vars - HashMap<String, Object> vars inside expression. Passively overload current R env variables.
        Returns:
        java cast Object Warning, UNSTABLE and high CPU cost.
        Throws:
        Exception
